text.section:
The Secretary of State may accept electronic signatures to meet the filing requirements for a:
Corporation as required in KRS Chapter 271B;
Nonprofit corporation as required in KRS Chapter 273;
Professional service corporation as required in KRS Chapter 274;
Limited liability company as required in KRS Chapter 275;
Partnership as required in KRS Chapter 362;
Partnership as required in Subchapter 1 of KRS Chapter 362;
Limited partnership as required in Subchapter 2 of KRS Chapter 362;
Cooperative corporations and associations as required in KRS Chapter 272 or 272A;
Business trust as required in KRS Chapter 386 or a statutory trust under KRS Chapter 386A;
Rural electric and rural telephone cooperative corporation as required in KRS Chapter 279;
Unincorporated nonprofit association as required in KRS Chapter 273A;
Assumed name filing under KRS Chapter 365; and
Filings under KRS Chapter 14A.
